'''热带风暴劳拉'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Laura}}）是[[2008年大西洋飓风季|2008年大西洋飓风季]]期间于9月29日在[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]中北部上空形成的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref>{{Cite web | editor = 张慧媛 | url = http://www.weather.com.cn/static/html/article/20081203/19160_2.shtml | title = 2008大西洋飓风季大盘点 | work = 中国天气网 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | date = 2008-12-03 | publisher = 中国气象局公共气象服务中心 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160602223337/http://www.weather.com.cn/static/html/article/20081203/19160_2.shtml | archive-date = 2016-06-02 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，也是该季第12场获得命名的风暴，虽然持续时间短，但规模却非常庞大。系统源自9月29日[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]以西约1635公里海域的大规模[[温带气旋|温带]][[低气压|低气压区]]，因行经洋面水温偏高而逐渐发展出热带天气系统特征。9月30日下午，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]认为劳拉已具备足够的热带天气系统特征，所以将之归类为热带风暴。

成为热带气旋后不久，劳拉又开始向温带气旋转变，并在10月1日上午完成转变过程，美国国家飓风中心至此发布针对气旋的最后一份公告。风暴残留继续移动，于10月5至8日分别在欧洲[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]、[[荷兰|荷兰]]和[[挪威|挪威]]产生暴雨并引发停电。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Laura 2008 track.png}}
9月26日，[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]以西数百英里洋面几乎没有移动的[[锋_(气象)|锋区]]沿线发展出[[温带气旋|温带]][[低气压|低气压区]]。这片低气压区逐渐增强，风速于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月27日中午12点达到每小时130公里，已达[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风标准。接下来几天里，低气压总体保持向西移动，在此期间逐渐失去锋面天气系统特征，开始转变成[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]。<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | date = 2009-02-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002011328/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL122008_Laura.pdf | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | title = Tropical Storm Laura Tropical Cyclone Report | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL122008_Laura.pdf | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | format = PDF }}</ref>9月29日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]认为低气压区已经发展出足够对流，因此将之归类成亚热带风暴劳拉<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | title = Subtropical Storm Laura Public Advisory One | year = 2008 | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.public.001.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184906/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.public.001.shtml | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  | dead-url = no }}</ref>。成为亚热带气旋后，劳拉的顶端云层开始将中心包裹起来，并在环流中心附近凝聚。对流围绕中心迅速组织，卫星观测结果表明气旋很可能强化<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | title = Subtropical Storm Laura Discussion One | date = 2008-09-29 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013128/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.001.shtml? | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。不过，之后的卫星观测结果表明，风暴此时风速已达到每小时95公里。系统总体结构仍属亚热带气旋，但也有逐渐发展出热带天气系统特征的迹象。<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Robbie Berg | author2 = Richard Pasch | title = Subtropical Storm Laura Discussion Two | date = 2008-09-29 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013732/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.002.shtml | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.002.shtml? }}</ref>

9月29日下午，卫星图像显示劳拉已发展出热带气旋特有的深层暖芯，但风场整体结构仍类似于亚热带气旋<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Robbie Berg | author2 = James Franklin | title = Subtropical Storm Laura Discussion Three | date = 2008-09-29 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305011953/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.003.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。当天夜间，风暴最强风场的半径收缩至130公里，同典型的亚热带气旋相比已经大幅缩小。但是，劳拉仍受到上层低气压区的影响，云系顶端依然单薄<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | title = Subtropical Storm Laura Discussion Four | date = 2008-09-29 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305200145/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.004.shtml }}</ref>。顶端云系的温度当晚逐渐下降，到次日早上时，风暴已处在转变成热带气旋的边缘，只是同上层低气压的强烈相互影响表明劳拉仍属亚热带气旋<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | title = Subtropical Storm Laura Discussion Five | date = 2008-09-30 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305200205/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.005.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.005.shtml? }}</ref>。虽然行经洋面水温降低，但水蒸气卫星图像表明风暴已同上层低气压分离，至此终于发展成热带气旋。劳拉在[[纬度|北纬]]40.6°海域成为热带风暴<ref name="TCR" />，相对典型的热带气旋而言要高很多<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Robbie Berg | author2 = Richard Pasch | title = Tropical Storm Laura Discussion Six | date = 2008-09-30 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.006.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305012843/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.006.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。成为热带气旋后不久，风暴又呈现出向温带气旋转变的迹象。气旋西侧开始有冷空气侵入，多个预测模型显示劳拉在次日早上逐渐转变成温带气旋，并且次日下午就已不再具备热带天气系统特征。<ref>{{cite report |author1=Robbie Berg |author2=Richard Pasch |title=Tropical Storm Laura Discussion Seven |date=2008-09-30 |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |work=National Hurricane Center |location=Miami, FL |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414174938/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.007.shtml |deadurl=no |accessdate=2016-04-29 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.007.shtml? |archivedate=2016-04-14 }}</ref>

[[File:Laura_29_September.jpg|right]]

夜间，风暴关联的对流开始消退并失去热带天气系统特征，但系统整体仍属热带气旋<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | title = Tropical Storm Laura Discussion Eight | date = 2008-09-30 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305200316/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.008.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.008.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。10月1日清晨，劳拉已开始全面朝温带天气系统转变。虽然还有热带特征，但风暴的云层格局已类似锋面天气系统，中心附近的对流也很少<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | title = Tropical Storm Laura Discussion Nine | date = 2008-10-01 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.009.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307221911/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2008/al12/al122008.discus.009.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-07 }}</ref>。由于气旋中心周围残存的雷暴活动和关联的降水都很少，气象机构于10月1日将风力仍达到热带风暴强度的系统降级成[[後熱帶氣旋|後熱帶氣旋]]。次日，劳拉的残留完全转变成温带气旋，然后开始重新强化并快速北上。10月3日清晨，风暴残留的移动速度在转向东进期间减弱，但风速提高到每小时120公里，已达飓风标准。系统加速东进，最终于10月4日在[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]以西数百英里洋面被更大规模的温带气旋吸收。<ref name="TCR" />

== 影响 ==
[[File:Laura_30_sept_2008_1655Z.jpg|thumb]]
劳拉在热带气旋阶段没有靠近任何陆地，所以没有造成人员伤亡或财产损失。风暴存在的绝大多数时间都位于开放水域，多艘船只和多个石油平台测得热带风暴强度大风。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}10月1日凌晨3点，呼号为“{{lang|en|VEP}}717”的石油平台所测风速最高，达每小时87公里。<ref name="TCR" />虽然气旋本身基本没有造成影响，但劳拉的残留在上层[[高速气流|高速气流]]的带动下转而逼近[[欧洲|欧洲]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Paul Simons | title = Weather: torrential rain expected as strong winds hit Wales and the South West | newspaper = ''The Times'' | location=London | date = 2008-10-04}}</ref>。[[大不列颠岛|英国]]部分地区因此在10月5日降下暴雨，引发局部洪灾。格里布路位于英格兰[[温德米尔|温德米尔]]附近路段的双边车道均被封闭，[[英国A65号公路|英国A65号公路]]位于老赫顿（{{lang|en|Old Hutton}}）到[[柯比朗斯代尔|柯比朗斯代尔]]（{{lang|en|Kirkby Lonsdale}}）之间路段也予关闭。部分地区的土壤含水量此前就已饱和，风暴排水渠不堪重负，导致局部地区洪水泛滥。[[英国M6高速公路|英国M6高速公路]]因路况不佳致使通行速度缓慢。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | title = Tropical storm brings floods | year = 2008 | newspaper = ''The Westmorland Gazette'' | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306165929/http://www.thewestmorlandgazette.co.uk/news/3728628.Tropical_storm_brings_floods/ | url = http://www.thewestmorlandgazette.co.uk/news/3728628.Tropical_storm_brings_floods/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>一名女性驾车进入洪水泛滥的街道后被困，必须依靠外界救援才得以脱身。面对暴雨，[[英国环境署|英国环境署]]共计发出76份洪灾预警和21份重大洪灾警报。<ref>{{cite news | author = Kaya Burgess | newspaper = ''The Times'' | date = 2008-10-06 | title = Met Office issues warning of more rain and floods | location = London}}</ref>

10月8日，劳拉的残留抵达[[荷兰|荷兰]]，其[[雨带|雨带]]此时开始同与[[挪威|挪威]]以西一片层次分明低气压区相连的[[冷锋|冷锋]]相互影响<ref>{{Cite news | author = Rob Sluijter | title = 5 oktober 2008: Wateroverlast in het noordwesten. | year = 2008 | publisher = ''KNMI'' | accessdate = 2012-11-15 | archivedate = 2012-11-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121115094616/http://knmi.nl/klimatologie/nieuws/wateroverlast_051008.html | url = http://www.knmi.nl/klimatologie/nieuws/wateroverlast_051008.html }}</ref>，在荷兰西北部降下113毫米雨量<ref>{{Cite web | author = Meteo Consult | title = De Noord-Hollandse 'zondvloed' nader bekeken. | year = 2008 | publisher = ''Meteo Consult'' | accessdate = 2011-07-24 | archivedate = 2011-07-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110724173418/http://www.weer.nl/nl/home/weer/weer_in_het_nieuws/weernieuws/archive/2008/october/ch/f2d584b038/article/de_noord_hollandse_zondvloed_nader_bekeken.html | url = http://www.weer.nl/nl/home/weer/weer_in_het_nieuws/weernieuws/archive/2008/october/ch/f2d584b038/article/de_noord_hollandse_zondvloed_nader_bekeken.html }}</ref>，导致部分民宅和街道被淹。降雨量还打破2006年当地创下的单日和10月雨量纪录<ref>{{cite news | author = KNMI | publisher = ''Meteo Consult'' | date = 2008-10-06 | accessdate = 2011-07-24 | title = De Noord-Hollandse 'zondvloed' nader bekeken | archivedate = 2011-07-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110724173418/http://www.weer.nl/nl/home/weer/weer_in_het_nieuws/weernieuws/archive/2008/october/ch/f2d584b038/article/de_noord_hollandse_zondvloed_nader_bekeken.html | url = http://www.weer.nl/nl/home/weer/weer_in_het_nieuws/weernieuws/archive/2008/october/ch/f2d584b038/article/de_noord_hollandse_zondvloed_nader_bekeken.html }}</ref>。缓慢经过挪威期间，风暴残留又重创该国电力设施，致使挪威南部部分地区有上万人失去供电<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nrk.no/nyheter/1.6247956 | date = 2008-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-04-29 | title = Kraftig uvær på Østlandet | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201403/http://www.nrk.no/nyheter/1.6247956 | publisher = NRK | author = Agnes Svalastog | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

